    # ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Jenkins Agent Secrets
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the JNLP secrets from Jenkins UI.
#
# How to get the secrets:
#   1. Start Jenkins controller: docker compose up -d jenkins
#   2. Open http://localhost:8080
#   3. Manage Jenkins → Nodes → New Node
#      - Name: python-agent-1
#      - Type: Permanent Agent
#      - # of executors: 2
#      - Remote root dir: /home/jenkins/workspace
#      - Labels: python
#      - Launch method: Launch agent by connecting it to the controller
#   4. Save — the secret appears on the agent's status page
#   5. Repeat for python-agent-2, builder-agent-1, infra-agent-1, infra-agent-2
#   6. Paste each secret below
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

PYTHON_AGENT_1_SECRET=acafa6a1f3be124d5ddfbdb27c9eb7bd6e36ef5874e59ca8899c8d1503c12cbe
